sistema

Class GestoreCinema

  • java.lang.Object
    • sistema.Persona
      • sistema.GestoreCinema

  • public class GestoreCinema
extends Persona
    GestoreCinema.java

    A representation of a Gestore Cinema; it extends the Persona.java class. A GestoreCinema has in addition the following attributes: username, password, email, cinema, autenticato.

    Author:
    Sara Martino
